  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Enhancing cooperation with the statistical institutions of the Russian Federation for improving UNIDO statistical products in the SDG context</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Earlier this year the Permanent mission of the Russian Federation sent a Note Verbal to UNIDO expressing its intention to renounce the appropriation of their share of unutilized balances for 2017 and allocate the funds to support the new strategic priority of UNIDO # #Strengthening knowledge and institutions#. Later in a meeting of the Director of PRS with the representative of Russian PM it was agreed that the resources could be utilized in statistical and analytical activities of PRS given the new mandate of the Organization in this area. Subsequently, the Permanent mission recommended three statistical and academic institutions to be included in project activities.</narrative>
  </description>
